    L = L_lmn[0]
    m = L_lmn[1]
    n = L_lmn[2]
    T = np.array(L_transform)
    L_transformed = np.dot(T, np.array([L, m, n]))
    if L_transformed[0] == L + L_transformed[0] and L_transformed[2] == 0:
        return 0
    else:
        lambda_val = L_transformed[0] - L
        return lambda_val
